+
+- Full details in `browser-views-patterns.md`
+- `browser:console-message` forwarded via `ipc-message` on parent WebContents — alive and working
+- `get_cookie_browsers` / `sync_browser_cookies` / `inject_browser_cookies` — REMOVED (no handlers existed)
+- `browser:getURL` / `browser:getTitle` / `browser:cookies:set` / `browser:cookies:get` — REMOVED (unreachable: not in allowlist, browserInvoke never called)
+- `ipc-message` event uses `...args` spread — correct arity
+- `sandbox: false` on views loading arbitrary URLs — ESM preload requirement, tracked as future improvement
+
